LinkElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMapElement\"><code>HTMLMapElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement\"><code>HTMLMediaElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLMetaElement\"><code>HTMLMetaElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMeterElement\"><code>HTMLMeterElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLModElement\"><code>HTMLModElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLOListElement\"><code>HTMLOListElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLObjectElement\"><code>HTMLObjectElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLOptGroupElement\"><code>HTMLOptGroupElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLOptionElement\"><code>HTMLOptionElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLOptionsCollection\"><code>HTMLOptionsCollection</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLOutputElement\"><code>HTMLOutputElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLParagraphElement\"><code>HTMLParagraphElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLPictureElement\"><code>HTMLPictureElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLPreElement\"><code>HTMLPreElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLProgressElement\"><code>HTMLProgressElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLQuoteElement\"><code>HTMLQuoteElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLScriptElement\"><code>HTMLScriptElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLSelectElement\"><code>HTMLSelectElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLShadowElement\"><code>HTMLShadowElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLSourceElement\"><code>HTMLSourceElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLSpanElement\"><code>HTMLSpanElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLStyleElement\"><code>HTMLStyleElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableCaptionElement\"><code>HTMLTableCaptionElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableCellElement\"><code>HTMLTableCellElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableColElement\"><code>HTMLTableColElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement\"><code>HTMLTableElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableRowElement\"><code>HTMLTableRowElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableSectionElement\"><code>HTMLTableSectionElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTemplateElement\"><code>HTMLTemplateElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTextAreaElement\"><code>HTMLTextAreaElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTimeElement\"><code>HTMLTimeElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTitleElement\"><code>HTMLTitleElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTrackElement\"><code>HTMLTrackElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLUListElement\"><code>HTMLUListElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLUnknownElement\"><code>HTMLUnknownElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLVideoElement\"><code>HTMLVideoElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HashChangeEvent\"><code>HashChangeEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/History\"><code>History</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Location\"><code>Location</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MessageChannel\"><code>MessageChannel</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PageTransitionEvent\"><code>PageTransitionEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Plugin\"><code>Plugin</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PluginArray\"><code>PluginArray</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PopStateEvent\"><code>PopStateEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RadioNodeList\"><code>RadioNodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><strong><code>WindowEventHandlers</code></strong> ミックスインは、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a>、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLBodyElement\"><code>HTMLBodyElement</code></a>、<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLFrameSetElement\"><code>HTMLFrameSetElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> などのいくつかのインターフェイスに共通のイベントハンドラを記述します。 これらの各インターフェイスは、追加の固有のイベントハンドラを実装できます。</span></p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>注</strong>: <code>WindowEventHandlers</code> はインターフェースではなく、ミックスインです。 実際には、<code>WindowEventHandlers</code> 型のオブジェクトを作成することはできません。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"プロパティ","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em><code>onXYZ</code> という形式のイベントプロパティは、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WindowEventHandlers\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>WindowEventHandlers</code></a> で定義され、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a> および Web Workers の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a> によって実装されます。</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onafterprint\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Window/afterprint_event\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onafterprint</code></a></dt>\n <dd><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/afterprint_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">afterprint (en-US)</a></code> イベントが発生したときに呼び出されるコードを表す <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> です。</dd>\n <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onbeforeprint\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Window/beforeprint_event\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onbeforeprint</code></a></dt>\n <dd><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/beforeprint_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">beforeprint (en-US)</a></code> イベントが発生したときに呼び出されるコードを表す <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> です。</dd>\n <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onbeforeunload\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Window/beforeunload_event\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onbeforeunload</code></a></dt>\n <dd><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/beforeunload_event\" title=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/beforeunload\">beforeunload</a></code> イベントが発生したときに呼び出されるコードを表す <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> です。</dd>\n <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onhashchange\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Window/hashchange_event\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onhashchange</code></a></dt>\n <dd><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/hashchange_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">hashchange (en-US)</a></code> イベントが発生したときに呼び出されるコードを表す <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> です。</dd>\n <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onlanguagechange\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Window/languagechange_event\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onlanguagechange</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/languagechange_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">languagechange (en-US)</a></code> イベントが発生したときに呼び出されるコードを表す <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> です。</dd>\n <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onmessage\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/message_event\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onmessage</code></a></dt>\n <dd><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/message\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">message</a></code> イベントが発生したときに呼び出されるコードを表す <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> です。</dd>\n <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onmessageerror\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Window/messageerror_event\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onmessageerror</code></a></dt>\n <dd><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/MessageError\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">MessageError</a></code> イベントが発生したときに呼び出されるコードを表す <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> です。</dd>\n <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onoffline\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"この項目についての文書はまだ書かれていません。書いてみませんか？\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onoffline</code></a></dt>\n <dd><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/offline_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">offline (en-US)</a></code> イベントが発生したときに呼び出されるコードを表す <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> です。</dd>\n <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.ononline\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"この項目についての文書はまだ書かれていません。書いてみませんか？\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.ononline</code></a></dt>\n <dd><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/online_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">online (en-US)</a></code> イベントが発生したときに呼び出されるコードを表す <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> です。</dd>\n <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onpagehide\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"この項目についての文書はまだ書かれていません。書いてみませんか？\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onpagehide</code></a></dt>\n <dd><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/pagehide_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">pagehide (en-US)</a></code> イベントが発生したときに呼び出されるコードを表す <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> です。</dd>\n <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onpageshow\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"この項目についての文書はまだ書かれていません。書いてみませんか？\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onpageshow</code></a></dt>\n <dd><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/pageshow_event\" title=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/pageshow\">pageshow</a></code> イベントが発生したときに呼び出されるコードを表す <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> です。</dd>\n <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onpopstate\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Window/popstate_event\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onpopstate</code></a></dt>\n <dd><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/popstate_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">popstate (en-US)</a></code> イベントが発生したときに呼び出されるコードを表す <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> です。</dd>\n <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onrejectionhandled\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Window/rejectionhandled_event\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onrejectionhandled</code></a></dt>\n <dd><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/rejectionhandled\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">rejectionhandled</a></code> イベントが発生したときに呼び出されるコードを表す <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> です。 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a> が拒否され、拒否が処理されたことを示します。</dd>\n <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onstorage\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Window/storage_event\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onstorage</code></a></dt>\n <dd><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/storage_event\" title=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/storage\">storage</a></code> イベントが発生したときに呼び出されるコードを表す <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> です。</dd>\n <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onunhandledrejection\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Window/unhandledrejection_event\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onunhandledrejection</code></a></dt>\n <dd><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/unhandledrejection\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">unhandledrejection</a></code> イベントが発生したときに呼び出されるコードを表す <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> です。 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a> は拒否されたが拒否が処理されなかったことを示します。</dd>\n <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onunload\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Window/unload_event\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onunload</code></a></dt>\n <dd><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/unload_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">unload (en-US)</a></code> イベントが発生したときに呼び出されるコードを表す <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> です。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"メソッド","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>このインターフェイスはメソッドを定義しません。</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/#windoweventhandlers\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ja\">WindowEventHandlers の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n   <td>最新のスナップショットである <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html51/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"HTML 5.1の仕様書\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 5.1</a> 以降、変更はありません。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html51/#windoweventhandlers\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 5.1<br><small lang=\"ja\">WindowEventHandlers の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">勧告</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"HTML Living Standardの仕様書\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard</a> のスナップショット。 <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"HTML5の仕様書\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5</a> スナップショット以降に <code>onlanguage</code> が追加されました。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/#windoweventhandlers\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"ja\">WindowEventHandlers の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">勧告</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"HTML Living Standardの仕様書\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard</a> のスナップショット。 <code>WindowEventHandlers</code> の作成（ターゲットの前にあるプロパティ）。</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.WindowEventHandlers","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/WindowEventHandlers/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a> と <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"プロパティ","id":"properties"},{"text":"メソッド","id":"methods"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"WindowEventHandlers ミックスインは、Window、HTMLBodyElement、HTMLFrameSetElement (en-US) などのいくつかのインターフェイスに共通のイベントハンドラを記述します。 これらの各インターフェイスは、追加の固有のイベントハンドラを実装できます。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WindowEventHandlers","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"WindowEventHandlers","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"WindowEventHandlers","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"WindowEventHandlers","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"WindowEventHandlers","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"WindowEventHandlers","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/windoweventhandlers","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/windoweventhandlers/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/WindowEventHandlers","title":"WindowEventHandlers"}],"pageTitle":"WindowEventHandlers - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}